name: CARD WHAT HELP YOU BOTH
description: Draw two cards, your opponent draws a card.

name: CARD WHAT MAKE BIG COMBO
description: For every two cards you've played this turn, inflict suspicion.

name: CARD WHAT CAN BUILD DECK FOR
description: Inflict suspicion for every time you've played this card this game.

name: CARD THAT IS GENERIC
description: Copy the effect of a card in your play area.

name: KIDNAP
description: Expel this card, gain a town card.

name: ITS BACK BABY
description: Pick two cards in the graveyard, shuffle them back into the main deck.

name: LETS GO GAMBLING
description: Reveal a random main deck card, copy its effect, reshuffle the main deck.

name: NOT GONE LOL
description: Reveal a random graveyard card, copy its effect.

name: MAGIC MISSILE
description: Roll the Die. If 3 or more, inflict 4 suspicion. Otherwise, self-inflict 2 suspicion.
